  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK489">
<l>eytaṟ kariya tiyaintakkā lannilaiyē</l>
<l>ceytaṟ kariya ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a rare opportunity occurs, while it lasts, let a man do that which is rarely to be accomplished (but for such an opportunity).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
